        "topic": "Nature & Action Traps",
        "question": "You see a beautiful mountain. You want to tell your friend to 'Look!' at it. Which tone should you use for 'Kan'?",
        "options": [
            "1st Tone (kān)",
            "2nd Tone (kán)",
            "3rd Tone (kǎn)",
            "4th Tone (kàn)"
