        "correct_answer_index": 3,
        "explanation": "Tone is everything! 看 (kàn - 4th tone) means to look. If you use the 3rd tone (kǎn), you are saying 'Chop!' or 'Cut!'. Telling your friend to 'Chop!' a mountain is a very different vibe than asking them to admire it!"
